description: Mango falooda, an easy, delicious, chilled layered dessert beverage made with mango puree, falooda noodles, basil seeds, mango ice cream & nuts
Aloo fry, an easy, quick, crispy potato fry made with less oil that makes a great side dish with rice and dal or sambar
Dal pakwan, a Sindhi food breakfast fare that consists of a crisp flat bread served along with a tasty chana dal drizzled with green chutney
Mushroom manchurian, a popular, restaurant style Indian Chinese mushroom starter that is simply delicious
Chilli mushroom, a restaurant style Indian Chinese mushroom starter that’s crisp with sweet, sour and spicy flavors
Strawberry pudding, an eggless, creamy dessert made with fresh strawberries and china grass or agar agar perfect for Valentine’s day
